721423f-a.title: Manhattan: Madison Avenue - 68th Street (East)
721423f-a.text:
815 Madison Ave., adjoining the N.E. corner of East 68th Street,
the Ginsburg and Levy Building was awarded first prise for the best
altered building in the Fifth Ave. Section in 1927.
Probably 1928.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
